sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Python as [ego-flow Python Package]
  participant Cache as [Local Cache]
  participant Backend as [Backend]
  participant DB as [DB]
  participant Storage as [Storage]

  Python->>Cache: CacheManager 생성
  Note over Python,Cache: root = EGO_FLOW_CACHE 또는 platformdirs user_cache_dir("ego-flow")<br/>server_root = {cache}/servers/{host-hint}-{sha1(api_base_url)[0:12]}<br/>repository_dir = repositories/{owner_id}/{repository_name}

  Python->>Python: manifest video artifact 선택
  Note over Python: selected fields<br/>video.video_id<br/>artifact.download_url<br/>artifact.size_bytes<br/>artifact.sha256<br/>artifact.content_type<br/>thumbnail.download_url optional

  Python->>Cache: ensure_video(client, repository, video)
  Note over Python,Cache: local path<br/>videos/{video_id}-{sha12}.mp4<br/><br/>download_mode != force_redownload이고<br/>파일이 존재하며 sha256이 일치하면 download 생략

  alt cached video valid
    Cache-->>Python: cached video path
  else cache missing or invalid
    Python->>Backend: GET /api/v1/repositories/{repoId}/videos/{videoId}/download
    Note over Python,Backend: Headers<br/>Authorization: Bearer ef_raw_python_static_token<br/><br/>download_url이 absolute URL, /api/ URL, /files/ URL 중 무엇이든<br/>EgoFlowClient._absolute_any_url()로 절대 URL화한다.

    Backend->>Backend: requireDashboardOrPython
    Backend->>DB: repository read 권한 + video 조회
    Note over Backend,DB: video.repository_id = repoId<br/>video.id = videoId<br/>video.status = COMPLETED<br/>vlm_video_path exists
    Backend->>Storage: video file 존재 확인

    alt not visible or file missing
      Backend-->>Python: 403 Forbidden or 404 Not Found
      Python->>Python: EgoFlowPermissionError or EgoFlowNotFoundError
    else artifact available
      Backend-->>Python: redirect or file response
      Note over Backend,Python: 현재 server download endpoint는 file-serving 경로로 연결되는 URL을 반환/redirect한다.
      Python->>Storage: artifact bytes download
      Storage-->>Python: video bytes
      Python->>Cache: tmp file write
      Python->>Python: sha256 검증
      alt sha mismatch
        Python->>Cache: tmp file 삭제
        Python->>Python: EgoFlowDownloadError
      else sha ok
        Python->>Cache: tmp file을 final path로 atomic replace
        Cache-->>Python: cached video path
      end
    end
  end

  opt with_thumbnails=true and thumbnail artifact exists
    Python->>Cache: ensure_thumbnail(client, repository, video)
    Note over Python,Cache: local path<br/>thumbnails/{video_id}.jpg<br/><br/>thumbnail은 sha256 검증 없이 존재 여부 기준으로 cache reuse
    alt cached thumbnail exists
      Cache-->>Python: cached thumbnail path
    else thumbnail missing
      Python->>Storage: GET signed thumbnail URL
      Note over Python,Storage: manifest artifacts.thumbnail.download_url<br/>예: /files/{owner}/{repo}/.thumbnails/{file}?signature=...
      Storage-->>Python: thumbnail bytes
      Python->>Cache: thumbnail 저장
    end
  end

%% 참고:
%% artifact download는 Python static token 기반 API 호출과 signed file URL download를 조합한다.
%% video artifact는 manifest sha256을 기준으로 cache 무결성을 검증한다.
%% thumbnail artifact는 현재 ego-flow-py에서 sha256 metadata가 없으므로 파일 존재 여부만 cache hit로 본다.
%% download_mode="reuse_dataset_if_exists"는 현재 코드상 cache 재사용 모드와 동일하게 처리된다.
